| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6036 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c36a3b6c-2ad9-5dbf-8db1-3890f64f117d"
